{"TopicId":207505,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"Is Refuelling a SSTO in orbit Cheating?","CreatedByName":"kangaroo3505","CreatedById":220374,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-01T17:26:17Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"kangaroo3505","CreatedById":220374,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-01T17:26:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI mean If you do refuel is it even considered an \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003Essto\u003C/abbr\u003E? Just wandering\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-01T17:28:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224110106\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207505\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221648833977\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022220374\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kangaroo3505\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, kangaroo3505 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI mean If you do refuel is it even considered an \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003Essto\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E? Just wandering\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E is Single Stage To Orbit. \u00A0Nothing in that description prevents refueling IN ORBIT. \u00A0It\u2019s already there.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerikBalm","CreatedById":91917,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-01T18:04:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot cheating at all, and still \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy SSTOs don\u0027t leave kerbin orbit. They stage to go beyond it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-04-01T18:05:23Z\u0022 title=\u002204/01/2022 06:05  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EApril 1, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by KerikBalm\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MythicalHeFF","CreatedById":176690,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-01T19:59:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u2019ve refueled SSTOs in orbit a few times\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022vriLv15.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/vriLv15.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"miklkit","CreatedById":201493,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-02T15:41:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr just fly to Minmus and refuel there.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022ceXOyGY.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022120.00\u0022 height=\u0022502\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/ceXOyGY.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"darthgently","CreatedById":204885,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-02T16:01:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224110106\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207505\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221648833977\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022220374\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kangaroo3505\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n22 hours ago, kangaroo3505 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI mean If you do refuel is it even considered an \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003Essto\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E? Just wandering\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, it is still an \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E = Single Stage To Orbit.\u00A0 If you refuel after achieving orbit it still only took a single stage, without refueling, to get to that orbit.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-03T17:28:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd lets get even more pedantic..\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 It doesn\u0027t have to be a spaceplane to be a \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E.\u00A0\u00A0 It just has to achieve orbit using only one stage.\u00A0\u00A0 One could make a (some what weak) argument that mode switching engines might constitute 2 different stages.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-04-03T17:29:26Z\u0022 title=\u002204/03/2022 05:29  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EApril 3, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by Gargamel\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerikBalm","CreatedById":91917,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-03T18:56:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224110974\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207505\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221649006880\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0One could make a (some what weak) argument that mode switching engines might constitute 2 different stages.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI wouldn\u0027t accept that argument, as nothing is discarded.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s not like a rocket (such as an eve \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E) that uses vectors/a mammoth initially, and then LV-Ns once in thinner air can\u0027t be a \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E, even though it used 2 different engine types.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s not what is meant by the term stage in rocketry afaik.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jimmymcgoochie","CreatedById":199902,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-04T15:01:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDefine \u201Ccheating\u201D.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo some people, just getting into orbit without needing more than one stage or boosters is cheating because what sort of unfathomable sorcery would be needed to pull off such an impossible feat; to others, using rocket engines that can do more than just on/off and which can be started more than once and in places other than the launchpad, and don\u2019t have to worry about propellant ullaging and boiloff to boot, is cheating because real rockets don\u2019t work like that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlay KSP the way \u003Ci\u003Eyou \u003C/i\u003Ewant to, don\u2019t let others tell you what\u2019s acceptable or not.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, and by definition an \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E just has to get to orbit in a single stage- a Kerbal with a jetpack is an \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E on Minmus. Going anywhere after that is irrelevant, so whether you need to refuel in orbit (as is planned for Starship going to the Moon/Mars) or can fly to somewhere like Minmus to refuel, or can just go anywhere at all using magic Kraken drives exploiting the weirdness in the game\u2019s physics systems, doesn\u2019t matter in the slightest bit. Making an \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E is the hard bit, anything else after that is a bonus.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerikBalm","CreatedById":91917,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-04T18:53:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224111290\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207505\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221649084475\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022199902\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022jimmymcgoochie\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, jimmymcgoochie said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ERo some people, just getting into orbit without needing more than one stage or boosters is cheating because what sort of unfathomable sorcery would be needed to pull off such an impossible feat\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n[Sarcasm]\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nConfirmed, playing stock KSP is cheating.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAt a minimum, you must play at a 3x scale to not cheat, preferably 6x or higher, and RP-1 or \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Realism Overhaul (mod)\u0022\u003ERO\u003C/abbr\u003E or whatever it is called to. And \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Ferram Aerospace Research (mod)\u0022\u003EFAR\u003C/abbr\u003E...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAll that, otherwise it is cheating\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n[/Sarcasm]\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Maria Sirona","CreatedById":210882,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-08T17:56:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nShort answer: No.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLong one: Not at all.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jcklemme","CreatedById":62597,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-09T10:48:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224111414\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207505\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221649098416\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002291917\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KerikBalm\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 4/4/2022 at 1:53 PM, KerikBalm said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n[Sarcasm]\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nConfirmed, playing stock KSP is cheating.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAt a minimum, you must play at a 3x scale to not cheat, preferably 6x or higher, and RP-1 or \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Realism Overhaul (mod)\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Realism Overhaul (mod)\u0022\u003ERO\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E or whatever it is called to. And \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Ferram Aerospace Research (mod)\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Ferram Aerospace Research (mod)\u0022\u003EFAR\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAll that, otherwise it is cheating\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n[/Sarcasm]\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Ferram Aerospace Research (mod)\u0022\u003EFAR\u003C/abbr\u003E is cheating.\u00A0 It makes it WAY easier to build planes and space planes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}